# Project Conventions

- use pnpm for package intalls
- Don't try to start the server, i will to this or assume its already running.

## Database Management
- All database schema changes should be made directly in the Supabase SQL editor
- No migration files are used in this project
- When making schema changes, document them in this file

## Code Organization
- API routes are stored in `app/api/`
- Database types and utilities are in `lib/db/`
- Components are in `components/`
- Server actions are in `actions/`

## Security
- Row Level Security (RLS) policies should be enabled for all tables
- Service role should be used for internal operations
- Authenticated users should have appropriate read/write permissions

## API Endpoints
- All API endpoints should be documented with their purpose and expected payload
- Use proper error handling and status codes
- Validate incoming requests

## Frontend
- Use existing UI components from the components directory
- Follow the established design patterns
- Keep components focused and reusable
